<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='274834' id='t-274834'>So how can the industrial Internet help here?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='278252' id='t-278252'>We've developed a preventive maintenance system</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='280887' id='t-280887'>which can be installed on any aircraft.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='282877' id='t-282877'>It's self-learning and able to predict issues</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='286128' id='t-286128'>that a human operator would miss.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='289084' id='t-289084'>The aircraft, while in flight,</span>
