<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='305557' id='t-305557'>helping seven million passengers</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='307519' id='t-307519'>get to their destinations on time.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
 5:21
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='310055' id='t-310055'>Or take healthcare.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='311708' id='t-311708'>Today, nurses spend an average</span>
