<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='316082' id='t-316082'>looking for medical equipment.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='317775' id='t-317775'>That seems trivial, but it's less time spent</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='322158' id='t-322158'>caring for patients.</span>
